OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FScotland's only oil        
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Frefinery due to cease      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fproduction                 
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Scotland's only oil refinery could     
OL,6, cease operations as soon as 2025 under 
OL,7, plans announced by owners Petroineos.  
OL,9,FThe company said Grangemouth had been  
OL,10,Ffacing significant challenges because  
OL,11,Fof global market pressures.            
OL,13,FPetroineos intends to turn the site    
OL,14,Finto a fuels import terminal which     
OL,15,Fwould result in the loss of at least   
OL,16,F400 jobs.                              
OL,18,FWork to transform the site is expected 
OL,19,Fto take 18 months.                     
